{
  "texts": [
    "By locally hosting a chatbot and providing access for all students, we can remove this barrier to access.",
    "One of the key challenges that must be overcome when implementing an LLM-based chatbot is course alignmentwe must be reasonably confident that student questions are answered in a way that aligns with the teaching goals of the course.LLMs are a recent technology capable of understanding natural language.",
    "At their core, LLMs are actually text-completion engines: an input is provided and the LLM is able to add to the input in a plausible, humansounding way [6].",
    "Most chatbots have been further trained in a process known as \"fine tuning\" to follow instructions, rather than simply complete or add to an input text.",
    "This process produces \"instruction-tuned\" LLMs, but the overall operation remains the samean input is provided, the LLM continues it."
  ]
}